---
description: Prisma + Supabase migrations
globs: prisma/**/*, package.json
---

- Never `prisma db push` for real environments; use `prisma migrate dev` locally; ship SQL; deploy runs `prisma migrate deploy` (via `postbuild`).
- `DATABASE_URL`: port **6543** (transaction pooler, app). `DIRECT_URL`: **5432** (session, migrations). DB user: `postgres.[project-ref]`.
